Class LogEntryLog4J

java.lang.Object
com.dua3.utility.logging.log4j.LogEntryLog4J
All Implemented Interfaces:
LogEntry
public final class LogEntryLog4J extends Object implements LogEntry
Represents a log entry with information about the log message, time, level, logger, and optional marker and throwable.
